Testing REST API locally:
1. Run the application locally in terminal ($ python3 main.py)
2. Open a new terminal window
3. Run the commands that you want to test, reference the POSTMAN samples on Piazza
   but change the hostnames to the local host address or deployed url
4. Run curl with -i flag if you want to see the status code along with response body


Package Create Testing:
curl -i --location --request POST 'https://ece461-project2.ue.r.appspot.com/package' \
--header 'X-Authorization: bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxMjM0NTY3ODkwIiwibmFtZSI6IkpvaG4gRG9lIiwiaWF0IjoxNTE2MjM5MDIyfQ.SflKxwRJSMeKKF2QT4fwpMeJf36POk6yJV_adQssw5c' \
--data-raw '{
	"metadata": {
		"Name": "Underscore",
		"Version": "1.0.0",
		"ID": "underscore"
	},
	"data": {
		"Content": "",
		"JSProgram": "if (process.argv.length === 7) {\nconsole.log('\''Success'\'')\nprocess.exit(0)\n} else {\nconsole.log('\''Failed'\'')\nprocess.exit(1)\n}\n"
	}
}'

Package Update By ID :
** Make sure to UPLOAD a package to the datastore, before you try to UPDATE the package.

curl -i --location --request PUT 'https://ece461-project2.ue.r.appspot.com/package/underscore' \
--header 'X-Authorization: bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxMjM0NTY3ODkwIiwibmFtZSI6IkpvaG4gRG9lIiwiaWF0IjoxNTE2MjM5MDIyfQ.SflKxwRJSMeKKF2QT4fwpMeJf36POk6yJV_adQssw5c' \
--data-raw '{
    "metadata": {
        "Name": "Underscore",
        "Version": "1.0.0",
        "ID": "underscore"
    },
    "data": {
        "Content": "",
        "URL": "https://github.com/jashkenas/underscore",
        "JSProgram": "if (process.argv.length === 7) {\nconsole.log('\''Success'\'')\nprocess.exit(0)\n} else {\nconsole.log('\''Failed'\'')\nprocess.exit(1)\n}\n"
    }
}'

AUTHENTICATE a user:
** make sure that there is an Entity for the user under: kind  = "user"

curl --location --request PUT 'https://ece461-project2.ue.r.appspot.com/authenticate' \
--data-raw '{
    "User": {
        "name": "ece461defaultadminuser",
        "isAdmin": true
    },
    "Secret": {
        "password": "correcthorsebatterystaple123(!__+@**(A"
    }
}'
